          <updateDate>2016-02-25T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Firm, Unwavering National Dedication to Water Act or the FUND Water Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Safe Drinking Water Act to reauthorize through FY2021 the drinking water state revolving fund program.</p> <p>The bill also amends the Federal Water Pollution Control Act (commonly known as the Clean Water Act) to reauthorize through FY2021 the state revolving fund program for water pollution control.</p>]]></text>
